  "title": "Abacus & Mental Arithmetic Teachers (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To conduct abacus, mental arithmetic classes (physical lesson and online lesson)</li>\n  <li>Supervise and motivate the learning of students</li>\n  <li>Proactively engage students and parents to communicate progress of learning</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum ‘O’ level or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Experienced in teaching abacus and mental arithmetic</li>\n  <li>Strong commitment and passion in teaching</li>\n  <li>Able to relate to children from preschool to primary school level</li>\n  <li>Possess enthusiasm, positive work attitude, and high energy</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekdays afternoon and/or weekends</li>\n  <li>Able to travel to different locations in Singapore</li>\n</ul>",
